    "This yields a 73-keyword network comprised of 6 distinct clusters.",
    "Figure 7 depicts the co-word analysis network with 73 nodes and 1121 edges.",
    "The size of a node is proportional to the number of occurrences it has with other nodes.",
    "The 6 clusters are colorcoded, with the red cluster containing 23 keywords and 138 occurrences of the main keyword \"scheduling\".",
    "The second green cluster contains 18 keywords, with \"project scheduling\" appearing 70 times as the main keyword."
